:1150983,"uid":241069,"like":198,"dislike":92,"score":106,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"慶祝樓主老母最後一次老母節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"樓主係戇鳩<br />\n不過今日唔好提人老母啦"},{"pid":"486f9d4617c92fad8855daf29fbbf9b5c9c3385b","tid":1150983,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f502a354d0b0dd92ca810e51ec78337295dfa97","tid":1150983,"uid":96182,"like":101,"dislike":7,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"唔通好似獌咁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無歐聯，球員星散，領隊無料，煞科日可以點面對？正常人都係繼續撐自己隊波，打返場好波。獌迷呢？<br />\n<br />\n今晚佢地只會關心白禮頓輸同狼隊贏。曼城係同市宿敵，利物浦就係世仇。兩隊爭冠，皇者曼聯只能哀求上天賜冠給同市宿敵，好讓利物浦繼續29年無冠。但係曼城由昔日弱者幾年間同皇者曼相差18個level，獌迷從無恥辱感，還繼續樂在其中，共享同市光榮。<br />\n<br />\n然後捱過煞科日，獌迷球季還未完結，佢地會繼續支持曼城贏足總盃，避免屈福特打歐霸而令皇者曼聯提早打第二圈外圍賽。<br />\n<br />\n捱過足總盃，獌迷就會化身車路士球迷，寄望車路士歐霸打敗阿仙奴，令自己不會成為Big six唯一一隊缺席歐聯的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n幾日後，獌迷就會做熱剌球迷，希望力阻利物浦六度歐冠封王。"},{"pid":"f318b61a519ed1fd3af51ef33f5f54efe0dd66f3","tid":1150983,"uid":248695,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"18b15d8d46ba590499cf674e09bce6e096a689a7","tid":1150983,"uid":241069,"like":198,"dislike":92,"score":106,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"慶祝樓主老母最後一次老母節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"今年最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa03bf9ee475383f17406f306b8d34c5880e803a","tid":1150983,"uid":248695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3d84de176e3ef4db9edaf07e5a594aa3d53981","tid":1150983,"uid":87155,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"citedB